    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Boil</strong> a kettle</p>\r\n<p><strong>Crush</strong> or chop the cashews coarsely</p>\r\n<p>Tip: Bash the nuts in their bag with a rolling pin for less mess</p>\r\n<p><strong>Peel</strong> and finely chop (or grate) the garlic</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
