    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Heat</strong> a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a matching lid with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">(2 tbsp)</span> olive oil over a medium heat</p>\r\n<p><strong>Once</strong> hot, add the cashew nuts, garlic, sultanas, baharat and turmeric with a large pinch of salt and cook for 1 min, stirring constantly</p>",
