      "instruction": "<p><strong>Add</strong> the couscous and stir for 30 seconds to coat in spice</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cover</strong> with 200ml <span class=\"text-danger\">(400ml)</span> boiled water and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>\r\n<p><strong>Once</strong> boiling, cover with a lid and remove from the heat&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Set</strong> aside covered until serving and the water has absorbed</p>",
